# Proposal

## What will (likely) be the title of your project?
"jumpy Bird"

## In just a sentence or two, summarize your project. (E.g., "A website that lets you buy and sell stocks.")
A rendition of flappy bird. 

## In a paragraph or more, detail your project. What will your software do? What features will it have? How will it be executed?
My rendition of flappy bird will start with a home screen with a play button and a high score(if available).
Then when the user presses the bird will render in and the map will begin moving with the obstacles coming
in from the right to the left. Everytime the user clicks the bird will go up "x" number of pixels to avoid hitting the obstacles.
For every ostacle the user succeeds in avoding, a point tracker in the top right will increase by one. For every five obstacles the user evades,
the obstacles will approach at a slightly faster speed. When the user collides with an object, I want a "Game Over" message to pop along with a "Go to Home"
and "Play Again" messages.

